title: Baboon - Face Down in Turpentine
description:
Baboon&#039;s excellent album, Face Down in Turpentine.  This was recorded in 1994.  It&#039;s difficult to describe their sound, and I&#039;ve never been good at describing music, anyway.  Back in 1994 they were a very loud band, and it&#039;s evident on this one.  There&#039;s a lot of punk influence in there, but sometimes they have a trombone in there and all kinds of shit.
